♪ Flooding through the hall ♪

896
00:41:55,467 --> 00:41:57,734
♪ Rising to the landing ♪

897
00:41:57,736 --> 00:42:01,671
♪ Tearing pictures from the walls ♪

898
00:42:01,673 --> 00:42:04,508
♪ The currents pull us underneath ♪

899
00:42:04,510 --> 00:42:08,145
♪ That bright tide rips us out ♪

900
00:42:08,147 --> 00:42:11,181
♪ Into a tangled coral reef ♪

901
00:42:11,183 --> 00:42:14,985
♪ Where we could never drown ♪

902
00:42:14,987 --> 00:42:17,921
♪ Now that ♪

